&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;&gt;There have been several threads on this.&amp;nbsp; It is felt that an increase in runspeed on all levels will improve our pulling capabilities.&amp;nbsp; The numbers that have been thrown around are 10-20% increase.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;5)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Reduce mend timer AA - &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Suggested Changed - &lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hastened Mend: 5 levels cost: 5,5,5,5,5 6% reduction per level.&lt;BR&gt;Mend = 6min refresh = 360 seconds. 6% = 21.6 seconds, 5 x 21.6 = 108 second, total refresh 4:12secs. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;It has been discussed that it would be a good idea to split among the levels instead of having to get to level 70 to be able to start working on these.&amp;nbsp; There has been some discussion over cost but no alternatives have been given so as of right now this is what is being proposes.&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;&gt;6)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;B&gt;Leather armor graphics&lt;/B&gt; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;O&lt;IMG height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif" border="0"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/O&lt;IMG height="16" width="16" src="/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif" border="0"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; Roman?? New ?Times 12pt;&gt;7)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;B&gt;Discipline stacking and timer issues.&lt;/B&gt;&amp;nbsp; A lot of monks feel throw stone should not be on the same timer as phantom lull and planes walk should not be with healing will.&amp;nbsp; Whirlwind also has a very long reuse timer and its tied to stonestance and earth walk, which are some life saving disciplines while pulling.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Currently being evaluated.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: Roman?? New ?Times 12pt; red;&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Suggested Changed - &lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;A solution to the timer issues is to keep them linked however, say when a monk uses whirlwind instead of waiting 40 min for stonestance to come back, it comes back in 4 min as if it was on its regular timer.&amp;nbsp; This will let us use our more power disciplins more often but will still keep it so we cannot chain use the disciplins.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;So if&amp;nbsp;whirlwind is used, both it and stone would grey out but stone would refresh as normal.&amp;nbsp; If stone was used&amp;nbsp;they would both grey out but since the quicker timer was the one used both would refresh as they do now.&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&#xD;
