&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in auto? mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; COLOR: red; **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: Roman??&gt;&lt;SPAN New ?Times FONT-FAMILY: 12pt; **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: COLOR: red; Roman??&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Propose Solution&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;: To &lt;SPAN&gt;insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&amp;nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&amp;nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&amp;nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
