&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt; #cccccc;&gt;10) &amp;nbsp;&lt;B&gt;Ranged item stats.&lt;/B&gt;&amp;nbsp; Monks have to lose stats while pulling due to losing their range item.&amp;nbsp; Some suggestions have been made of using only the ammo slot to throw from.&amp;nbsp; Putting more monk throw able items in game with good stats with a drop rate which makes them a viable pulling tool instead of a rare stat item.&amp;nbsp; More trade skill items with stats so they can be made and sold.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;This is a revised item.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp; New information was passed along, no new development feedback.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in TEXT-ALIGN: 0pt; auto? justify; mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: red; New ?Times Roman?? COLOR: **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: 12pt;&gt;Propose Solution: To &lt;SPAN&gt;insure that the ammo slot is used as the primary sorce of expendeture of thrown items.&amp;nbsp; With this, place throwing weapons in the game with appropriate stats to be used in the range slot.&amp;nbsp; The ammo should not have to be the same as the thrown weapon and the highest range should be used for distance.&amp;nbsp; These items used for stats should be no-drop and level required to prevent tweeking.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/