&lt;P class=MsoNormal auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0pt; 0in justify; TEXT-ALIGN: **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: #cccccc; FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? 12pt; ?Times New&gt;5)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;B&gt; Return Kick AA&lt;/B&gt; - &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?FONT-SIZE: FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? 12pt; ?Times New red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN FONT-FAMILY: COLOR: Roman?? 12pt; ?Times New **SMURF**?FONT-SIZE: red;&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;The issues with Return Kick and double reposit is known by development and we do have plans to fix it.&amp;nbsp; Currently we do not have a time frame on when these AA's will be fixed.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
